snippet.title: FIFA 20 | Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Experience FOOTBALL INTELLIGENCE in FIFA 20 with new Gameplay features that put you at the centre of every match: http://x.ea.com/59039

Pre-order the FIFA 20 Ultimate Edition before August 5th and get an untradeable FUT 20 Ones to Watch Player Item: http://x.ea.com/59040

FIFA 20 launches worldwide September 27 on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC, bringing two sides of The World's Game to life - the prestige of the professional stage and an all-new authentic street football experience in EA SPORTS VOLTA.

Subscribe to see more FIFA 20 videos: http://bit.ly/pzw4VD. 

#FIFA20
